description: xtg-data-sqlclient is a simple library that allows you to connect with sql server.
summary: This library contains four asynchronous methods: ExecAsync: execute a setence in sql server. ExecQueryWithoutParamsAsync: execute a query without parameters. ExecQueryWithParamsAsync: execute a query with parameters. ExecProcedureDataTableWithParamsAsync: execute a stored procedure with parameters.
title: XTG.DataBase.SqlClient
